# Installation

## Mini conda or anaconda

### Note: On the Aouizerat mac anaconda was installed


## Update anaconda

conda update --prefix /opt/anaconda3 anaconda


## Update conda (This should be updated, but just run it again)

conda update conda


## Install wget

conda install wget


## Download the latest qiime2
wget https://data.qiime2.org/distro/core/qiime2-2021.11-py38-osx-conda.yml


## Create the QIIME2 environment

conda env create -n qiime2-2021.11 --file qiime2-2021.11-py38-osx-conda.yml

### OPTIONAL CLEANUP
rm qiime2-2021.11-py38-osx-conda.yml


## Activate the conda environment
conda activate qiime2-2021.11


## Check if Qiime is installed correctly
qiime --help

### Should show the possible options and usage


## If using Bash, Run this command to enable tab completion:
source tab-qiime


## for zsh

#### autoload bashcompinit && bashcompinit && source tab-qiime
